jab likha hua hai 

🕹️ keydown aur keyup kya karte hain?
🔽 keydown → Jab tum key dabate ho, ye turant detect karta hai
🔼 keyup → Jab tum key chhodte ho, tab ye detect karta hai

🧠 Yaad rakhne ki simple trick:
Soch le:
🕹️ Keyboard ek switch hai.
Jab switch dabaya → keydown hua
Jab switch chhoda → keyup hua

📱 Daily life example:
Jaise mobile ka volume button:
Jab dabata hai → awaz badhti jaati hai → keydown
Jab chhodta hai → awaz badhna ruk jaata hai → keyup

🔢 Code samajh:
let bricks = [];
for (let c = 0; c < brickColumnCount; c++) {
  bricks[c] = [];
  for (let r = 0; r < brickRowCount; r++) {
    bricks[c][r] = { x: 0, y: 0, status: 1 };
  }
}

📌 c ka matlab:
Yahan c ka matlab hai column (satoon) — yani brick ke ustadon ke line.
Aur r ka matlab hai row (qatār) — yani brick ke upar se neeche tak ke layer.



🔁 Sochne ka tarika:
Cheez	   Example	                                Sochne ka tareeka
Canvas	    canvas	                                 Board ya khaali page
Context	    ctx = canvas.getContext("2d")	         Brush/pencil
Drawing	     ctx.fillRect(...), etc.	             Drawing action



🔁 Simple Analogy (Drawing ek shape ka step-by-step):
beginPath() → Chalo naye shape ki shuruaat.
arc() ya rect() → Shape banaya.
fillStyle = "red" → Color set kiya.
fill() → Rang bhara.
closePath() → Drawing complete.

